Class TypeErasureProcDecls

java.lang.Object
polyglot.visit.NodeVisitor
polyglot.visit.HaltingVisitor
polyglot.visit.ErrorHandlingVisitor
polyglot.ext.jl5.visit.TypeErasureProcDecls
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Copy<NodeVisitor>
public class TypeErasureProcDecls
extends ErrorHandlingVisitor
This class rewrites method decls to change the type of arguments and the return value so that the appropriate override relationships will hold in Java 1.4. Also adds in new MethodDecls to match the erased signature of any overridden methods.
